o though, and I have no idea what skill you need to do it. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>In the same tradeskill-ranged machine that you find the arrowheads, you'll find the metaplast arrow-shafts that you combine them with. I haven't yet run into a machine that didn't sell both, but YMMV (was looking in adv and superior shops...dunno if they're in basics). I have no idea what skill the combo required however...I hear it's based on Int, but can't confirm.<br><br>Got them to shoot w/a Sapphistic bow. Poison Bamboo was...not very impressive. 169 damage...whoopee. I suppose I should try out the fire ones before I completely write these off, but I don't know that I want to burn IP on BSA based on what I've seen thusfar. If I could punch with a bow equipped I might feel differently <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bthepunchingbag74708.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=publius>Publius</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Martial, Baby, MARTIAL.</span><br>  Posts: 412<br> <font color=#660000>(3/11/02 10:42:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=468.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bow Special arrows....how do they work?</span><hr size=1> So what we need now is a special MA-only bow that depends 50% on MA skill <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>And it could be a unique item, from an MA-only quest!<br><br>YES! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezbo